@Löwen.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7197/api/Notification
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Create notification
POST {{Löwen.Api_HostAddress}}/create-notification
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": "8a56d232-5b5e-4e3d-9df5-61c92d36a77e",
  "title": "New Message",
  "message": "You have a new message from admin.",
  "isRead": false,
  "createdAt": "2025-10-12T12:30:00Z"
}

###

### Get notification by ID
GET {{Löwen.Api_HostAddress}}/get-notification-by-id?id=b5b3a1e8-91ab-4d6c-981a-6e612ccf0455
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get notifications by user
GET {{Löwen.Api_HostAddress}}/get-notifications-by-user?userId=8a56d232-5b5e-4e3d-9df5-61c92d36a77e
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Delete notification
DELETE {{Löwen.Api_HostAddress}}/delete-notification?id=b5b3a1e8-91ab-4d6c-981a-6e612ccf0455
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
